    <h1>Free tax calculators built for quick estimates</h1>

    <p>
      MyTaxCalcs is a free tax calculator website designed to help users estimate
      common U.S. tax situations, including federal income tax, state income tax,
      self-employment tax, sales tax, and capital gains tax.
    </p>

    <h2>Our goal</h2>
    <p>
      The goal of MyTaxCalcs is to make tax estimates easier to understand.
      Instead of only showing a final number, our calculators are designed to show
      taxable income, deductions, estimated tax, withholding, refunds, and amount owed
      in a simple format.
    </p>

    <h2>What MyTaxCalcs does not do</h2>
    <p>
      MyTaxCalcs does not provide tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice.
      Tax rules can change, and every taxpayer’s situation is different. Always
      verify results with official tax sources or a qualified tax professional.
    </p>

    <h2>Current calculators</h2>
    <p>
      The site currently includes a federal income tax calculator and state calculator
      pages for all 50 U.S. states. Additional tools for self-employment tax,
      sales tax, and capital gains tax are planned.
    </p>

